.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, baking, cooking, woodworking, card-games
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, scooter, tram, skateboard, motorbike
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
House: palace, tower, cape-cod, wooden, ranch-style
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, horror, action, sports, animation
1. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is cooking
2. the person driving the swedish is the person watching action movies
3. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking coffee
6. the cape-cod house is the person watching horror movies
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the tower house
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies
11. the person watching animations movies is on the left or right of the tower house
12. the palace house is the person drinking beer
13. the person driving the tram is the wooden house
14. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening
15. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person drinking water

